<h1>Your Week In Review</h1>
<p>Here&apos;s a quick rundown of the key data points from <a href="<%= @web_url %>/app/sites/<%= @site.id %>/dashboard"><%= @site.name %></a> last week:</p>

<p><b>Overview</b></p>
<p>Total visitors: <a href="<%= @web_url %>/app/sites/<%= @site.id %>/visitors"><%= @data[:total_visitors] %></a> <i style="color:#A0A0A0">(<%= @data[:new_visitors] %> new)</i><br />
Total recordings: <a href="<%= @web_url %>/app/sites/<%= @site.id %>/recordings"><%= @data[:total_recordings] %></a> <i style="color:#A0A0A0">(<%= @data[:new_recordings] %> new)</i><br />
Average session duration: <b><%= @data[:average_session_duration][:formatted] %></b> <i style="color:#A0A0A0">(trending <%= @data[:average_session_duration_trend][:direction] %> <%= render 'shared/trend', locals: { direction: @data[:average_session_duration_trend][:direction] } %><%= @data[:average_session_duration_trend][:trend] %>)</i><br />
Pages per session: <b><%= @data[:pages_per_session][:formatted] %></b> <i style="color:#A0A0A0">(trending <%= @data[:pages_per_session_trend][:direction] %> <%= render 'shared/trend', locals: { direction: @data[:pages_per_session_trend][:direction] } %><%= @data[:pages_per_session_trend][:trend] %>)</i><br />

<p><b>Trends</b></p>
<p>Busiest day: <b><%= @data[:busiest_day] %></b><br />
#1 indirect traffic source: <a href="<%= @data[:biggest_referrer_url] %>"><%= @data[:biggest_referrer_url] %></a><br />
#1 country: <b><%= @data[:most_popular_country] %></b><br />
#1 browser: <b><%= @data[:most_popular_browser] %></b><br />
Most popular visitor: <a href="<%= @web_url %>/app/sites/<%= @site.id %>/visitors/<%= @data[:most_popular_visitor][:id] %>"><%= @data[:most_popular_visitor][:visitor_id] %></a><br />
Most popular page: <a href="<%= @site.url %><%= @data[:most_popular_page_url] %>"><%= @site.url %><%= @data[:most_popular_page_url] %></a></p>
